Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,13,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,13,,Did you ever experience it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,13,,Two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,13,,A startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,13,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,13,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,13,,With a Taishou Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,13,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,13,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,13,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,13,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.10,Default,,0,0,13,,High, High, High,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,13,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,13,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After a messy night at a bar, our High Collar Lady{大乱闘の夜は更けて年々コロリをハイカラさん }
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,had sweet, sweet dreams on Shinobu's back.{少尉の背中で甘い甘い夢を見る}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A romantic breeze blows between the two betrothed{ロマンチックなそよ風が2人の間を吹き抜けて}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and even the opposing count approves their relationship.{お家はこれで反対と伯爵不災もついフォロー}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a problem.\NPerhaps, a quirk of fate.{ところがどっこいこれが運命のいたずらか}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,An unexpected villain received the previous night's bill.{思いもかけない悪役にゆうべのつけが届いたからさあ大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of evil revenge is he plotting now?{少尉に対する復讐がいかなる嵐を呼ぶのやら}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:05.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&}Sublieutenant ❤ Benio {少尉 紅緒 - the same ai ai kasa as in episode 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good, huh.{こうなっちゃうから嫌よね}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For real. I'd like to write my name here.{ほんとここや私の名前を書きたいもんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief... Though in every aspect,{まったくね人間的にはベニオさんよりも}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we're more charming that her, right?{私たちの方がグーンと魅力的ですもんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! {そういうこと人間の運命って悲しいわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We might have a chance some time!{そのうちチャンスがあるかもよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? I've known her since I was born,{ん?何よ、こっちはおにゃーっと生まれた時から}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't be this way.{長い付き合いなんだから、もう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&} Ranmaru ❤ Benio {蘭丸}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's right!{こうこなくちゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so worried about?{何をくよくよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh willow by the river...{川端柳 }
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like I don't get Ranmaru's feelings,{まあ、蘭丸の気持ちは分からねえでもねえがな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but it'll be bad if someone else in here sees this.{屋敷の人の目に触れると穏やかでねえな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's change it, just in case.{いっそのことを、この方がまだ様になら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:09.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&} Ushigorou ❤ Benio {牛五郎}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But it could put Boss in trouble...{しかし、親分は迷惑するな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it gotta be harmless, I'll do it like this.{ま、当たり障りのないところなら、こんなところかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.21,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&} Ushigorou ❤ Kisaragi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna say that it's hard to be together!{\b1}{??? idk}{ふたりとは、つらいねってなことをおっしゃりたいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.62,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&} Ushigorou ❤ Kisaragi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is this...{ああ、なんだっけ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd feel bad, destroying his dreams.{でも、あの男のせっかくの夢を壊すのも気の毒。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep it there.{そっとしといてやりましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:04:01.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8E6E2&\bord0\b1\blur0.667}Episode 20\N{\fs66.667}Who Are the Two Under the Love{ Divination} Umbrella? {相合傘のお二人は? - I hate that we can't explain what exactly is this umbrella without resorting to an8 tl-notes}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How shameful, having all of these love letters...{まったくいやらしいったらあれしない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? More love letters fo Shinobu.{あまた正位のところラブレター}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. They keep on coming every day.{そうなの毎日こうですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen a playboy like him?{あんなプロイボーイ見たことない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you'd better keep an eye on Shinobu, okay?{benioんいい加減で少尉を見かぎった方が身のためじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So does he read them thoroughly and answer everyday?{少尉は毎日目を通して一日返事を書くの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't read them and he tosses them straight away.{全然 読み も し ない で 一直 線 に 散り 間 を 行き}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's the difference between them not coming at all?{一つも来ないのと同じじゃないのでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Benio so kind?{ベニオさんてどこまで人がいいんだか}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps she's defending Shinobu?\NI gotta watch out!{それとも少尉を弁護してるんだこれは要注意}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Ranmaru- err, Ranko.{やあ、らんまるーえ、いや、蘭子君}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your letters.{お手紙です}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw them away for me.{捨ててくれたまえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.{ではお言葉に従って}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hold on a second.{あちょっと待った}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now, throw the rest.{ いいよ捨てて}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need anything?{何かご用はございませんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.{別に}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, fine by me.\NThen, tomorrow at three, at our usual place.{いいですよ ではいつものところで明日の3時に}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow at three, at our usual place..."\NThis is bad!{いつものところで明日の産地大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too shabby, considering it's mine.{我ながらいい出来場へ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,B-B-Benio! It's awful, it's awful!{ペニョさん 大変大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, they fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my masterpiece!{人の傑作を}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can arrange all the flowers that you want later,{花くらい後でいくらでも僕が生けてあげるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something more important right now!{それよりも一大事なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Ijuuin appointing a date\Nwith a sender of one of the love letters, via phone!{少尉はラブレターの相手と電話でおデートの約束をしたんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But didn't you say \Nhe doesn't read any of his love letters?{あらだってshouiはラブレターは読まないんじゃなかったの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an exception,{例外が登場したの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,understand me!{しっかりしてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And who was the sender?{ 相手は誰なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't manage to see that,{そこまでは目が届かないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do detective work.{僕は探偵じゃないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it might just be a harmless letter,{じゃあそれは何でもない手紙で}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sender might have been a man.{相手は男の人かもしれないじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was definitely a woman, I can't be mistaken.{絶対女性よ私にはピンとくるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman's instinct never fails.{女の直感て外れこないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'm right. Must be so!{そうよきっとそうだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman's instinct, huh?{女の直感ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, tomorrow at three,\NIjuuin is seeing this sender{とにかく明日の3時shouiはいつものところで相手と会う いつものところっていうのがくせものだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"at their usual place," he said, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you think through everything that much,{でもねそんなことに一々神経を尖らせたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,there'll be no end!{キリがないでしょ }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, but I decided that I'd protect you no matter what,{そうでも僕はベニオさんを守るって決心したんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so just leave this to me!{ま、任せといて}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I can't get if that guy's a boy or a girl.{まったくあの子って女だか男だか分かりゃしないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Let's try once again from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at three, at our usual place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoui... The sender is a man, isn't he?{SHOUI相手は男の人よね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's {\i1}got{\i0} to be man.{そうよ男に決まってるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though all his letters are from women...{毎日毎日女の人だとして}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Benio, you've got a call.{ベニオ様お電話です}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? For me? Who is it?{私に誰から}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll learn it yourself, once you answer it.{出ていただければお分かりになるそうです}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be? Maybe Nanny. Or it might as well be Tamaki.{誰かしらばあやかなそれともたまきかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? It's Hanamura Benio.{もしもしhanamura benioですが}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm the women's duty teacher from the Girls' School Atonashi.{もしもしこちら後なし女学科の受け持ち教師で ございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? It's you, teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Be respectful!{先生で悪ございましたね - Didn't understand}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean it-{いえそういうわけでは}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, you haven't been at school in a long while,{花村さんこのところ欠席が目立ちますが}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,are you feeling unwell, by chance?{お加減でも悪いのざんすか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that I've been through a lot...{いえただいろいろと取り込みが続きまして}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I think it's better for you to come back at school,{ならばご出席なしたほうがよろしいかと存じますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,frankly speaking, your grades are terrible,{率直に申しまして成績がかんばしからくやもしれません}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you have too many absences and this is a serious issue for your school year.{集積にだと学年?最悪な事態かもしれません}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by serious?{最悪だと言いますと}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That you'll fail!{落第}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood! I'll be back from tomorrow onwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I got behind on so much homework...{こんなに宿題が溜まっちゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio? Still not coming to bed?{べにおさんまだ休まないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you have to be ready by three.{明日は3時に大変なのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about the Shinobu matter.{shouiのことなんかかまっちゃいられないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave this homework undone.{ダメなの宿題が溜まっちゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I help you out?{手伝いましょうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,English, maths, history, religion, science and writing, which one do you pick?{英語と数学と歴史と宗教と科学と 漢文のうちそれだけやってくれる?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night!{おやすみなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done all of my homework in one night!{宿題を全部やっちゃうなんて }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so good!{心気よくだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be {3時の件大丈夫 }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Still worried about that?{まだそんなこと言ってんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine!{平気平気}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm going to be late.{ああ、うっかりして遅刻だな}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisaragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about my breakfast, I have to go to school!{朝ごはんなきにして 早く学校行かなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've done all of the homework! Look!{宿題全部やったのよほら}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You do know it's Sunday, don't you?{本日は日曜日でございますが}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shinobu has to be there by three o'clock, then he'll go out at two.{3時にどこかで敵と会うアウトして shouiは2時頃にはここを出るね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Likely.{だろうな}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Ushi, you'll be following Shinobu.{そしたらウィッシュさんはSHOUIの後を そーっとつけるのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don'tcha think it'd be better if I took his neck{うーん いっそのことをSHOUIの胸ぐらを 締め上げてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I asked who the hell he's boutta meet,{3時に会う相手はどこのドイツだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,until he just blurts it out?{ 吐かせりゃ一苦労じゃねえかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no delicacy, don't you?{デリカシーがないのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Cacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Never heard 'bout that.{おいらもは出きれいでよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's for Benio's sake.{いいからいいから 何事もベニオさんのためなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you saying that you don't care{それともうしさん、ベニオさんを不幸せにして}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,about Benio?{構わないって言うの?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no! Say it again, I dare you!{やえ!もう一遍言ってみろ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's somebody that won't make her sad,{親分に泣きを見せるような奴は、}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,then that guy is me, Ushigorou!{俺がただじゃおかねえ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Boss's best partner!{このうしごろ様が相手だってんだい!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna kill me! Let me go!{苦しく、あ、離して、あ、}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have to discover Shinobu's true persona,{だったら、この際少尉の人柄をとことん突き止めるのも}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's for Benio's sake, got it?{ベニオさんのためって分かるでしょ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Alright, gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you stay here until it's two,{だからUshiさんは2時頃までここで頑張って}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,then you follow Shinobu wherever he goes, got it?{SHOUIを絶対に尾行するのよ絶対よ }
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for Boss, I'ma do everything!{親分のためならえんや頃だ任しとけって}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don'tcha doubt me!{任せておけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a long time since I went shopping!{久しぶりにショッピング}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like this, going out to relax is the best.{こういう時には気晴らしに出かけるのが一番よね }
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I might go to Minatoya in Gofukubashi.{福橋の港屋にでも行ってみようかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Year 1913, the artist Takehisa Yumeji opens Minatoya, his print shop,{大将2年 竹下ゆめじ御福橋に港屋を開店}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,which was wildly power among girls.{少女の人気を集めた}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I might see Takehisa Yumeji's new work.{竹下ゆめじの新しい絵が出てるかもしれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me, I'll catch that Sublieutenant in no time.{今に見てろshouiの尻尾をしつかんでみせるぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Boss.{あっああああああああ おやぶん}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I benefit from your service?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Err, wait, I can't!{そりゃその アンキー}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No service today.{やめた}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's go, Ushigorou.{ああやってushigorou}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, actually, I, uhm...{それがそのでございましてあの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so hesitant for?{何をグズグズしてるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you know, it's that...{いえねえ 実はねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you see, I can't today.{ベニオさんよなにいいんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If something's wrong, just say it.{何か事情でもあるのなら言いなさいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothin' serious, really!{大したこっちゃないのよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just hurry up and start moving!{なら早く言ってよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go...{あらよっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, can't you speed up a bit?{ushigorou何をもっとしょっきっとできないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah-yeah, yeah-yeah.{ええええええ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, you've turned into a Edoite?{なあによそれでもえどっこなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be one!{そうこなったらやけだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's going out, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he now?{どこ行ったのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Ushi?{あの牛さんを}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about Ushigorou,{ushigorouならほんの少し前}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,he went out with Benio a while ago.{ベニオさんのお供をして出かけたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be going.{それじゃあ出かけてくるからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you too!{あたしおともしまーす}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko. Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ushigorou.\NI'll come back on my own, so don't worry about it.{ご苦労様丑五郎、あとは一人で何とかするからもういいわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what time is it?{時に今何時ですかねー ]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it should be about three.{さんじょまあってるんじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu and Kichiji...{ショイとキチチさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At three, somewhere, with someone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's betraying me!{shouiが私を裏切るね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I trusted him...{信じていたのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I trusted him!{信じていたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But why do I have to hide here and act oblivious?{嫌だったし なんだってこんなところに隠れたりしたんだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right,{そうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to say something and interrupt them.{堂々と出て行って声をかけたっていいんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should I say exactly?{でもなんて言って声かけたらいいのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, "Hello"?{えーっとこんにちは}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else, "the weather is so clear today".{えっと、えっと、え、本日は誠にお日柄もよく}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it sounds like a set phrase.{、なんだか結婚式のスピーチみたいだし、えっと、}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{[?]月が啼いたかほととぎす- a Japanese poem or something - maybe substitute it with something else}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, won't work.{ああ、こりゃだめだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, otherwise, going straight to the point...{それともそれともうん、それとも担当直入に、}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!{おっ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,Never mind{\c&H312FC5&\3c&HE2DFD9&\b1\blur0.667}  {でもないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, never mind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:16.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,Never mind{\c&H312FC5&\3c&HE2DFD9&\b1\blur0.667}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, never mind, never mind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:23.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3926DB&\3c&H4E403C&} Panicking {じたばた}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't stop anymore!{あらあららら わわわ 止まんなくなっちゃった}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&HE2DFD9&\b1\blur0.667} Panicking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop, stop! I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:26.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,Never mind{\c&H312FC5&\3c&HE2DFD9&\b1\blur0.667}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop, I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:28.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&HE2DFD9&\b1\blur0.667} Panicking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop!\NWhoa, stop, stop, stop! Stop!!!{うわああ 止めてよ止めてよ 止めて止めて止めて}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&HE2DFD9&\b1\blur0.667}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master...{若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen between you and Lieutenant Innen?{印念中佐と何か面倒なことでも}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With Lieutenant?{中佐と?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When he invited me to the tatami room the other day...{この間お呼ばれしたお座敷で}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the Sublieutenant Ijuuin{時々ここへ来るんだろ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,come here often?{伊集院少尉}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are quite close, in fact.{はいご引きに願っております}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know that he has a fiancee?{知らんのかい彼に婚約者がいることを }
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:17:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...{そうですか - is that so sounds wrong 'cause theoretically she already knows}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, with Hanamura's daughter.{しかも花村の娘だそうな}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that...{中佐が}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.{そうですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then something happened, right?{何かあったんですね }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, somewhat.{まあ少しばかり}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.{お気をつけてくださいまし }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lieutenant is prone to holding grudges{中佐はあの通り、根に持つお人柄}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's very influential in the Army,{陸軍将関係にも顔の利くお方ですし}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so something irreparable might happen...{何か取り返しのつかないことでも起こったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, it's all good.{まさか大丈夫ですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be harsh, but I doubt that he'll be{中佐にしてもあのような些細なことで}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so mad for a thing like that.{いつまでも気を悪くなさってるなんて思えない }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for worrying about it, though.{あなたが心配してくださるのはありがたいけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!{若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What could they be talking about?\NI can't hear them.{何話しているのかしら聞こえない}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happened to you, Young Master, I...{もしも若様に何かあったら私}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise{申し訳ございません}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said that.{言ってはならないことでした}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kichiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So those two... after all, they are...{やっぱり、やっぱりあの二人が}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!{若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kichiji, please let's break all of this.{吉次何も言わずに別かれてくれ }
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what men tell to geishas, right?{別れろきれろは芸者の時に言う言葉}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer if you told me to die right now.{今の私にはいっそ死ねと言ってください}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kichiji, please forgive me.\NI am betrothed to a fiancee.{きちじ 許しておくれ 私には押しつけられた許婚がいるのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pug-nosed and too ugly too look at,{ちんくしゃで目も当てられない女だが }
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to endure this for my grandmother.{おばあ様のために耐えねばならない}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kichiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, get lost, get lost!{ちれちれちれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, don't touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What, was it just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so concerned about those two that they even appear in my dreams.{夢にまで出てくるんだから あたしてそーっとあの二人のこと気にしてるんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But why am I so worried about it?{でもなんで夢でまで悩まされるのよ }
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, if it has to happen, let's turn these dreams in my favour.{そうだ 夢なら私に都合のいいように}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have sweet dreams!{バラ色なのみなっちゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good, Ranmaru, set the mood!{いいぞいいぞ蘭丸、気分出して}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, forgive me.{許してくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I am betrothed to a fiancee.{私には押し付けられた許婚が いるのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pug-nosed...{ちんくしゃで}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut! Cut, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really like that line,{そこんとこの台詞から 気に入らないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,change it, got it?{台詞返せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, forgive me.{許しておくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a beautiful fiancee that I deeply love.{私には心から愛している 素晴らしい許婚けがいるのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cute, smart,{可愛くて頭がよくて}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,has a unique personality,{人柄も抜群で}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I don't even deserve her.{私にはもったいないくらいの窓もあぜる}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master...{若さま}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you ever again.{君とは二度と会いたくない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's part and pretend none of this ever happened.{今日までのことはなかったと思い すっぱり別れておくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's such a wonderful girl,{そんな素晴らしいお嬢さんでは }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then I don't stand a chance against her.{私などとても太刀打ちできません}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gracefully step aside.{いさぎよく身を引きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you understood it?{分かってくれたか}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. However...{はい その代わり}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However?{その代わり}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me see how splendid that girl is{そのお嬢さんがどんなに立派なお方か}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with my very eyes.{一目合わせてくださいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.{いいと思う }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone call me?{誰か呼んだか}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you, Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I always making a fool of myself?{あたしだけどうしていつもずっこけるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, those two make for a fantastic couple.{何しろしろ向こうは美男美女様になってたもんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always been a way better match than me.{私なんかよりずっと似合ってた}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, who is going to be the one under the Love Umbrella{あいあいがさに寄り添って少尉と肩を並べるのは}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,side by side with Shinobu?\NWho will be laughing in the end?{一体どこの誰なのか 最後に笑うものは誰なのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, High Collar Lady!\NThings have yet to be decided!{なくな負けるなはいからさんでたとこ勝負の夢がある}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:23:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fast asleep or awake, Benio can't help but think about Shinobu and Kichiji,{寝ても覚めてもしょういときちじの面影はベニオの脳裏から消えやらず}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point her appetite is long gone.{人もいぶかる食欲不振}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.63,0:23:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a fool for being trustful?\NOr is the deceiving side in the wrong?{信じた自分がバカなのが騙す向こうが悪いのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble after trouble,{悩み悩んで挙句の果てに}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio has finally made up her mind{ついにベニオは決意した}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time in Here Comes the High Collar Lady: \NLife is Short, Yet Riddled with Worries.{命みじかく悩み果てなく} Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,13,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,13,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that period
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,13,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,13,,I just want to know what's in his heart, \Nwhile he goes away{added} I want him to turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,13,,to give me once again this loving glance{made up to better match song pacing}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,13,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have this unrequited feeling{/This unfulfilled wish is heavy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,13,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,13,,Just a tomboyish lady with a smidgen of pretension
